00:01:40.167 --> 00:01:43.737
FAR BEYOND THE SPRAWL
  OF SUBURBAN AMERICA,

00:01:43.804 --> 00:01:46.573
WHERE SUCCESS AND FAILURE
  COLLIDE,

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:48.875
