00:53:03.247 --> 00:53:06.550
YEAH, WE'VE BEEN HERE NOW
 FOR 27 YEARS.

00:53:06.617 --> 00:53:08.619
IT'S A GOOD PLACE.
 YEAH.

00:53:08.686 --> 00:53:11.455
WE'VE DONE
  A LOT OF BUSINESS HERE.

00:53:11.522 --> 00:53:13.123
BUT WE'RE GETTING READY
 TO SELL IT.

00:53:13.190 --> 00:53:14.725
I THINK WE'RE--

00:53:14.792 --> 00:53:17.628
I'M JUST ABOUT GETTING TOO OLD
 TO RUN A RESTAURANT.

00:53:17.695 --> 00:53:19.063
I DID A LOT OF FISHING,

00:53:19.129 --> 00:53:20.364
A LOT OF HUNTING
  ON THE SALTON SEA.

00:53:20.431 --> 00:53:23.434
IT'S BEEN A WONDERFUL
  RECREATION AREA,

00:53:23.500 --> 00:53:26.303
AND WE HOPE IT WILL BE
  THAT WAY AGAIN.

00:53:27.805 --> 00:53:28.772
Eva Worthy:
  CATHY!

00:53:28.839 --> 00:53:30.007
Cathy:
 YEAH.

00:53:31.308 --> 00:53:35.512
I NEED TWO CHEESE OMELETS,
A SHORT STACK...

00:53:35.579 --> 00:53:37.147
I'M GOING TO BE
 IN THE UNEMPLOYMENT LINE

00:53:37.214 --> 00:53:39.850
HERE SHORTLY.

00:53:39.917 --> 00:53:42.486
GOD, I'VE WORKED
 HERE FOUR YEARS.

00:53:42.553 --> 00:53:44.822
FOUR YEARS;
I'M SURE GONNA MISS IT.

00:53:44.888 --> 00:53:46.523
THERE'S PEOPLE
 THAT HAVE BEEN COMING HERE

00:53:46.590 --> 00:53:48.025
FOR 20 YEARS,

00:53:48.092 --> 00:53:50.027
JUST TO COME IN AND HAVE A CUP
 OF COFFEE IN THE MORNING,

00:53:50.094 --> 00:53:51.795
EVEN IF IT'S FOR FIVE MINUTES
 AND LEAVE.

00:53:51.862 --> 00:53:53.530
THEY'VE BEEN DOING IT
 FOR 20 YEARS.

00:53:53.597 --> 00:53:55.432
AND SO IT'S GONNA BE
 A CHANGE FOR 'EM.

00:53:55.499 --> 00:53:58.902
LIKE LEONARD, HE COMES IN,
  HE FILLS UP MY ICE THING,

00:53:58.969 --> 00:54:00.137
BEFORE I EVEN GET THERE,

00:54:00.204 --> 00:54:03.774
AND HE'S GONE
 BEFORE THE PLACE EVEN OPENS UP.

00:54:03.841 --> 00:54:06.910
THEY'VE BEEN GOOD FRIENDS
 AND GOOD COMPANY,

00:54:06.977 --> 00:54:10.080
AND I'M GONNA MISS 'EM.

00:54:11.782 --> 00:54:13.083
WELL, I'M GLAD THEY'RE CLOSING,

00:54:13.150 --> 00:54:14.852
AND THEY CAN'T CLOSE
 SOON ENOUGH,

00:54:14.918 --> 00:54:20.457
BECAUSE I'VE GOTTEN USED TO
 'EM NOT BEING THERE ALREADY.

00:54:20.524 --> 00:54:22.626
THEY'RE THE HIGHEST-PRICED
PLACE IN TOWN.

00:54:22.693 --> 00:54:24.862
...SAYS YOU'RE GONNA TAKE
 THE TAPE OFF AND BURN IT.

00:54:24.928 --> 00:54:27.931
NO, I SAID
TAKE THE TAPE OFF.

00:54:27.998 --> 00:54:28.966
DO YOU'RE THING!

00:54:29.032 --> 00:54:31.668
OH, SHUT UP.
 ( Laughing )

