( Smack )

00:54:32.803 --> 00:54:34.104
SO I CAN
TAKE THE TAPE OFF!

00:54:34.171 --> 00:54:36.073
I SAID I'M DONE.

00:54:36.140 --> 00:54:39.309
HE'S GONNA MISS IT;
 HE LOVES IT.

00:54:39.376 --> 00:54:41.512
I MEAN, OBVIOUSLY,
  YOU'RE 91 YEARS OLD

00:54:41.578 --> 00:54:43.380
